            "id": 6009943,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 久禾光(6498)大漲7.34%，報117元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>久禾光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6498:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6498\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6498-TW</a>)06日12:15股價上漲8元，報117.0元，漲幅7.34%，成交492張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>久禾光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6498:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6498\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6498-TW</a>)所屬產業為光電業，主要業務為各式光學鏡頭之加工製造買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌9.92%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.02%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-97 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-39 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-58 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
